  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Proton pump inhibitors act in blocking acid secretion and also have antioxidant and
      anti-inflammatory properties. For that mechanisms possibly PPIs may have an anti-inflammatory
      action with improvement in skin lesions in patients with psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Proton pump inhibitors act in blocking acid secretion and also have antioxidant and
      anti-inflammatory properties. For that mechanisms possibly PPIs may have an anti-inflammatory
      action with improvement in skin lesions in patients with psoriasis.

      The study will assess the evolution of skin lesions in psoriasis patients using PPIs
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
